Greg,

I just installed Deluxe trim on a '75 restoration. I got all the  
window seals and trim from Wolfsburg West. They all fit perfectly and  
are of high quality.

Their site is hard to get around in, so I recommend having them send  
you a color catalog.

Jon Stiles

